--------------------
----- DV VIDEO -----
--------------------

There are 2 main DV video formats:

DV-PAL: 720x576 pixels @ 25 fps  (1000 frames = 40 Seconds = 144 MB)
DV-NTSC: 720x480 @ 29.97 fps  (1000 frames = 33.33 Seconds = 120 MB)

For more info about DV video see:

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DV
https://www.adamwilt.com/DV.html

